Description_lang: When Capacitor Totem fades or is destroyed, another Capacitor Totem is automatically dropped in the same place.

description_blz.en_US: When Capacitor Totem fades or is destroyed, another Capacitor Totem is automatically dropped in the same place.

description_blz.de_DE: Wenn das Totem der Energiespeicherung abläuft oder zerstört wird, erscheint automatisch ein neues an derselben Stelle.

description_blz.ko_KR: 축전 토템이 사라지거나 파괴될 때 자동으로 같은 위치에 또 다른 축전 토템이 생성됩니다.
